An S-1 switch adds new pickup voicings to the American Elite Tele. And features like a 9.5"-14" compound-radius fretboard make these guitars effortless to play. The Fender American Elite Telecaster is the future of one of the most popular workhorse guitars ever. This pre owned Tele is a killer player with wonderful action and all of the spank and twang that you would expect out of a good Tele.
